item_name: Dell Optiplex 3090 Desktop Computer Micro PC Intel Core i5 10th Gen i5-10500T 8GB Ram 256GB M.2 SSD
item_desc:
Dell Optiplex 3090 Desktop Computer Mini PC Intel Core i5 10th Gen i5-10500T 16GB Ram 256GB M.2 SSD

-Intel Core i5 2.30 GHz processor provides you the solid performance to watch videos, play games, and on the same node its adaptability makes you more productive

-16 GB DDR4 SDRAM memory to handle complex applications simultaneously
